ta-sc-zrtbni-1 edgoES"><p class="ArticleCard__Author-sc-zrtbni-2 KIAzD">By Anton Bitel</p></div><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/lists/10-great-robot-films" title="Read 10 great robot films" class="ArticleCard__CallToAction-sc-zrtbni-4 fwpHHm"><span>10 great robot films</span></a></article><article uuid="7b527ca6-ec22-40ea-8503-80725e8b4d30" image48x27="https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2021-05/2001-a-space-odyssey-1968-keir-dullea-space-suit-inside-craft.jpeg/96x54-cropped/2001-a-space-odyssey-1968-keir-dullea-space-suit-inside-craft.jpeg" standfirst="To infinity and beyond... Celebrate 60 years of human spaceflight with our countdown of awe-inspiring space movies." class="ArticleCard__Outer-sc-zrtbni-0 eIZIIS articleCard Lists"><div class="ArticleCard__CategoryTag-sc-zrtbni-7 yMPPW">10 great</div><div class="ArticleCard__PageImageContainer-sc-zrtbni-5 ehvIXQ"><div class="ArticleCard__PageImage-sc-zrtbni-6 goyhok image"></div></div><h3 class="ArticleCard__Heading-sc-zrtbni-3 bynrVe">10 great films about space travel</h3><div class="ArticleCard__Meta-sc-zrtbni-1 edgoES"><p class="ArticleCard__Author-sc-zrtbni-2 KIAzD">By Brogan Morris</p></div><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/lists/10-great-films-about-space-travel" title="Read 10 great films about space travel" class="ArticleCard__CallToAction-sc-zrtbni-4 fwpHHm"><span>10 great films about space travel</span></a></article><article uuid="f20fa9db-8b2f-4f3e-aeec-6a37539c1a03" image48x27="https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2021-04/color-out-of-space-2019-parked-car-against-purple-trees.jpg/96x54-cropped/color-out-of-space-2019-parked-car-against-purple-trees.jpg" standfirst="Enter the mouth of madness with these films inspired by the cosmic horror tales of H.P. Lovecraft." class="ArticleCard__Outer-sc-zrtbni-0 eIZIIS articleCard Lists"><div class="ArticleCard__CategoryTag-sc-zrtbni-7 yMPPW">10 great</div><div class="ArticleCard__PageImageContai